PRETORIA – A new local lipstick brand may give international names a run for their money. The line of lipsticks called "Fancy Sapphire" was started by third-year student, Mmatlala Mabotja. It has now turned into a small business, which she is hoping, will extend into make-up and other beauty products. Watch Moneyline’s Mpho Nakana's interview with Mabotja above. eNCA